<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Password Change Successful</title>
  <style>
    /* Add your custom styles here */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .warning {
      padding: 10px;
      background-color: #ffdddd;
      color: #c00;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Password Change Successful</h1>
    <p>Hello {{ name }},</p>
    <p>Your password has been successfully changed for your account.</p>
    <p>If you initiated this password change, you can ignore this email.</p>
    <div class="warning">
      <p><strong>Warning:</strong> If you did not request this password change, it is possible that someone else has accessed your account without authorization. In such cases, please take the following steps:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Contact our support team or an admin immediately to report the unauthorized activity.</li>
        <li>Reset your password to ensure your account's security.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
    <p>Thank you,</p>
    <p>The Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
